    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic composure. This unit has been curated to meet our rigorous standards for quality and performance, ensuring a sophisticated driving experience. Well-maintained and thoroughly inspected, it offers an exceptional balance of longevity and value for the serious motorist. We invite you to evaluate its superior handling and refined interior firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
