      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great and drives smoothly. It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you'll love how it handles!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving unit features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS, delivering 333 hp through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is reinforced at the subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional lateral grip. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain tight and responsive. A driver-focused machine for those who value analog feedback and engineering purity.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained interior. Clean title. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint maintains a high gloss, although close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the driver-side door edge. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only slight curb rash on the rear passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows light bolstering wear on the driver's seat but remains free of rips or stains. All technological features, from the navigation system to the premium audio setup, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quiet and strong, backed by a comprehensive service log showing on-time oil changes and a recent transmission fluid flush. The tires offer plenty of life for the seasons ahead. This is a dependable, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready for the road.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent performance and refined engineering. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Ideal for the discerning driver seeking a balance of luxury and long-term reliability, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience. We invite you to acquire a machine that has been curated for excellence and sustained value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! Honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable ride and I\u2019ve truly enjoyed every mile in it. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for something dependable and stylish without that brand-new price tag. It runs like a charm and is totally ready for its next road trip. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver: a 2011 Porsche Cayman S (987.2) featuring the robust 3.4L DFI flat-six powerplant and a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This mid-engine chassis offers exceptional balance, further enhanced by a recent refresh of the suspension geometry and a set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The hydraulic steering rack provides communicative feedback, while the four-piston monobloc calipers ensure consistent threshold braking performance. Mechanically sound with a documented service history addressing the water pump and drive belt tensioners. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains taut and the bores have been scoped clean. An ideal candidate for the enthusiast seeking a pure, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
